   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,888:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 1. Project Overview 
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,889:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,889:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Problem Statement
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,889:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,890:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Domain:
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,891:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Healthcare / Disease Diagnosis.
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,892:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,892:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Problem Statement:
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,901:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Early detection of diabetes is critical for effective management and preventing
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,905:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: severe complications. However, initial symptoms can be subtle and often go unnoticed. Our project
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,906:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: aims to predict the risk of early-stage diabetes based on patient demographics and reported
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,907:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: symptoms.
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,907:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,907:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Solution Approach:
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,911:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  We developed an end-to-end Machine Learning pipeline utilizing an ensemble
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,912:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: learning technique to predict diabetes risk, integrated with a full-stack web application for real-time
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,912:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: inference.
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,913:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 2. Dataset Collection 
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,913:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,914:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Utilization
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,914:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,914:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Source:
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,915:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  We used a secondary dataset named 
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,915:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: diabetes_data_upload.csv
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,917:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  (aligning with the
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,918:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: UCI Early Stage Diabetes Risk Prediction dataset).
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,918:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
