   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,936:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Polydipsia (Excessive thirst), Sudden weight loss, Weakness, Polyphagia (Excessive
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,938:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: hunger), Genital thrush, Visual blurring, Itching, Irritability, Delayed healing, Partial
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,939:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: paresis, Muscle stiffness, Alopecia (Hair loss), Obesity.
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,939:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
