   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,950:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: operates by constructing a multitude of decision trees during training and outputting the mode of the
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,951:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: classes.
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,951:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
