   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,958:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: feature) and passed the rest of the variables directly to the Random Forest model.
   DEBUG: 2026-07-05 19:55:54,958:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 4. Training Process 
